subject: College World Series
Baseball (College)
Baseball
lead_paragraph: C. J. Hinojosa broke the College World Series’s long home run drought in the seventh inning, Chad Hollingsworth and Travis Duke limited U.C. Irvine to four hits, and Texas won, 1-0, in an elimination game in Omaha.
